testcase.name: Unit: App App Abstract Route redirects a user that is not logged in
KudosCtrl should not let a user give a kudos to themselves
KudosCtrl calls add kudos when saveKudos is called
Controller: Login should display an error message on bad login
Controller: Login should display success message on good login
Controller: Login should call the authentication service with the right parameters
Controller: MainCtrl should set the last kudos for the user if they are logged in
Controller: MainCtrl should not set the last kudos for the user if they are not logged in
Controller: MainCtrl should set lastSentNotificationDismissed cookie when clicking hide notification
Controller: MainCtrl should set notificationDismissed when the cookie is present
Controller: RegisterCtrl should allow a user to register
Controller: RegisterCtrl should set the failure message to the message returned by the authentication service
Controller: UsersCtrl should have a list of users on the scope
